The paper focuses on deep learning approaches for cardiac image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) research. The use of multi-task learning and atlas propagation also suggests a potential fit for multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
